text: Vicki Harber (born 28 July 1956) is a Canadian rower. She competed in the women's quadruple sculls event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Canada Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Ottawa
